{"type": "article", "id": 29062, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-07-03T23:00:22Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 14485, "name": "Mischer’Traxler"}, {"id": 29710, "name": "Gavin Coyle"}, {"id": 29711, "name": "Fermob"}, {"id": 29712, "name": "Lyon Béton"}, {"id": 18315, "name": "Matali Crasset"}, {"id": 29713, "name": "Bertrand Jayr"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160704023844LT308KSH7PJrAoCa.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h3>Equilumen by Mischer’Traxler</h3>\n<p>维也纳的双人设计组合 <a href=\"http://www.mischertraxler.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mischer’Traxler</a> 把天平和灯具结合在一起，打造出了一款名为 <a href=\"http://www.mischertraxler.com/projects_equilumen.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Equilumen</a> 的吊灯，希望以此表现平衡性带来的美感。在长棍两侧各安装了一个球形灯，同一个金属圆圈相连。当长棍处于平衡状态时，两边会发出亮度相同的灯光。如果拉动圆圈破坏了平衡，更低一端的灯光会变得明亮而被抬高的灯则会变暗，像是把光传导到了另一侧，很有趣味。Equilumen 曾在今年的米兰设计周上展出，目前还未投入生产。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704030703mQBswIydngUDRrVC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607040307475Yh293etFAjcHkvd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704030820aLqIAd2UVbvsp9kJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704030903oa8wuqtDHbXIQN4r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704030949HMyUc3v1Kz0jIO46.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704031020Ort03aiwH5CTkvgs.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Zigzag by Gavin Coyle</span></h3>\n<p>位于伦敦的 <a href=\"http://gavincoyle.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gavin Coyle</a> 工作室一直致力于通过环保的制作方式打造美观耐用的产品，这个名为 Zigzag 的菜板系列是工作室的最新产品。菜板的部份由枫木制成，分为三种不同的形状，手工定型后进行了涂层处理以展现哑光的质感。手柄的材质有胡桃木和樱桃木两种可选，而被称作 Zigzag（锯齿）也是因为手柄与菜板相连处的细节。无论是将三件组合还是单独悬挂在墙上，不同木材间的搭配都能带给人一种简洁清新的感觉。这是它的<a href=\"http://gavincoyle.co.uk/projects/shop/chopping-boards/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 80 英镑。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704031207eXcKuSq36JBwokW0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704031252TKMyDwjbsp81vXaL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607040313299rBSI7Hj6fgMECVO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704031400vM6Ou4BHLyiW5Rdl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.698044\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704031437CdGo4Y0L6nXvsfRV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.682152\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704031505mRo1uFnpbf4zYBQv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.699267\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Stripe chair by Matali Crasset</span></h3>\n<p>喜欢条纹和缤纷的色彩？<a href=\"http://www.matalicrasset.com/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">Matali Crasset </a>为法国的花园家具制造商 <a href=\"http://www.fermob.com/fr/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fermob</a> 设计的 Stripe 花园椅会让你眼前一亮：一改传统座椅采用的垂直放置的设计，Crasset 将铝制的拉伸板纵向放置，就像是一条优雅的曲线从上至下延伸，仿佛为座椅覆盖上了柔软的织物，提高了舒适性。Stripe 有一系列明亮鲜艳的色彩可选，能够为各类室外或者室内环境增添不一样的活力。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704031748dwN2P8ba3SOftlWV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.322263\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704031925JbousfXHOzarFqTY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.377751\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704032156pHXthIfQv7TiW9Ju.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704032233f52UHTuicySBRJnV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.760391\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704032354Dg1ZwyOlYLaHJfXQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.760391\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704032419Y1C6Hu8lLMPIxwhS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Dandelion by JungHoon Lee</span></h3>\n<p>空中飘扬的蒲公英通常是春天来临的信号，然而我们现在很少有机会直观地感受到气候变化，往往都是通过或大或小的屏幕了解天气信息，JungHoon Lee 为此设计了一款以蒲公英为灵感的天气装置 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/38823793/WEATHER-OR-NOT\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dandelion</a>，让人们可以用手感受到室外的风力与温度。它通过无线网络与智能设备相连以读取天气的相关数据，随后将他们转化为通过触觉感知的互动信息。Dandelion 内置了制冷/热模块和一个小风扇，当你用手触碰装置时，风扇会模拟风力以及温度让孢子摇晃，气氛灯也会根据温度点亮。虽然它不能提供精准的数字，但通过这种方式换新衣橱也是个有意思的选择。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704032519dEfeQ3McOzDF97ov.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704032549f3jamr1cH7uBkKTi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607040327220VkOzegYPrxEBbRm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704032759lpdOA0JRzmg7WxrQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607040328267GVhLNB6mTEOxRWu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704032853QORpcSjkitYDrU4H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Life in Progress by Bertrand Jayr</span></h3>\n<p>法国艺术家和设计师 Bertrand Jayr 最近为 Lyon Béton 用混凝土打造了一系列极简而美观的家饰，今天介绍的 Life in Progress 时钟就是其中的一款产品。光滑的钟面上并没有作任何数字标示，仅通过两根指针和十二个缺口表现时间。它不仅能够简单地放置在任何平面，内置的四根铝尺允许你随意地将它悬挂在墙上。这是它的<a href=\"http://us.lyon-beton.com/store/concrete-accessories/life-in-progress-clock/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 123 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704033025aN7RruQUyqOTD28n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704033059Aa4p6ljm1EhJeG7k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704033143HweTNQcG1KfkuImU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704033217SWk94R7V05NzjGUA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704033246EmYjI8DyOAkKJ5zB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704033325KdwuYrRz5Qt0vqTp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704033406ImZbY9oDUO6JkzqX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h3><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Teawith kettle by Keren Hu</span></h3>\n<p>城市中的居住空间越来越小了，这在皇家艺术学院毕业生 <a href=\"http://www.rca.ac.uk/students/keren-hu/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Keren Hu</a> 看来，意味着通常会与他人共享空间的年轻人们将需要更多小巧且功能齐备的物件，为此他设计了一款桌上电水壶 Teawith，打破了客厅与厨房的边界，让人不再受限于灶台旁。水壶上方是一个铝制的提梁，弧形结构让握持变得更加舒适顺手，放下时只要按下提梁就能够开启烧水功能。无论是醒来后的第一杯水、办公桌上的一杯咖啡，还是两三好友相约的下午茶，Teawith 都可以满足日常需要，干净利落的外观让它不会再被冷落，可以大大方方地摆上桌面。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704033634wVeHRiN8j9T0UcJo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704033702VhcwpDQX20OJARiE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704033728Eivw3ZSUFV9rz5os.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607040338034P1bTCkzuF7EjRtB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704033836bwSp0o2gRsnyJiXl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704033903EJ4j7DcXVg92uMTK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n"}